<template><div><h1 id="autocomplete" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#autocomplete"><span>Autocomplete</span></a></h1>
<p>A searchable input component with dropdown suggestions. Supports both remote API calls and local option filtering.</p>
