<h3 id="remote-api-call" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#remote-api-call"><span>Remote API call</span></a></h3>
<p>When <code v-pre>fetchOptions</code> is provided, the component fetches results from a remote API. This takes priority over the <code v-pre>options</code> prop.</p>
